{{alias}}( str[, ...args] )
    Inserts array element values into a format string and prints the result.

    Parameters
    ----------
    str: str
        Format string.

    ...args: Collection|*
        Collections or values.

    Examples
    --------
    > var log = require( '@stdlib/array/log' );
    > var x = [ 1, 2, 3 ];
    > var y = [ 4, 5, 6 ];
    > log( '%d < %d ', x, y );
    // e.g., => '1 < 4\n2 < 5\n3 < 6\n'
